b) loan.py should contain function apply_loan(amount)that accepts a loan amount and prints a confirmation message with the amount.
Write a python program to import modules from banking package and demonstrate both functions.


# account function
def open_account(name):
    print("Account created for", name)

# loan function
def apply_loan(amount):
    print("Loan applied for amount:", amount)

